column2: SELECT o.ra, o.dec, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_beta_flux, g.nii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.sii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux_err, g.sii_#_flux_err into mydb.dr1#_mpa_jhu_# FROM MyDB.MyTable_# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.objra, m.objdec, #) AS n JOIN specphotoall AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN galspecline AS g ON o.specobjid = g.specobjid
